已經唔係走唔走既問題<br />\n而係明知自己就算真係拎個心出黎講<br />\n人地都唔會真係想聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n心諗&quot;痴線 做咩要無啦啦聽你呻仲要比意見<br />\n我又唔明你做咩咁頹&quot;<br />\n唯有口講&quot;唉...你唔好唔開心啦 我係到嘛&quot;<br />\n<br />\n習慣左唔同人講 又要比人屌我收收埋埋<br />\n痴鳩線架啲人真係</blockquote><br />\n其他人有事，我好盡力付出時間同心機去開解佢哋<br />\n到我想搵人傾，願意聽既，一個都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37894b49dec4c568bcc5cf83489f420808e6569b","tid":419817,"uid":64277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T14:57:43.000Z","msg":"我應該要去死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f763d75b13b2dfae16518e8e51fe2822579bb3e1","tid":419817,"uid":21260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T15:52:01.000Z","msg":"點解到有人可以陪你 你又要激走人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}